{"tid":549380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新田購物城今試業僅一成開舖　遊人稱「被搵笨」","createTime":"2018-02-03T14:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T05:59:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":135,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b642f25ef50cf94329ddbc53c769685f94729b","tid":549380,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8f13f7229443ef5688b14083052c672c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8f13f7229443ef5688b14083052c672c.jpg&h=7f078bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由民建聯立法會議員黃定光牽頭的新田購物城，今天首日試業，場內僅有約一成店舖開業，另只有小量正在裝修，其餘仍空置。有市民在網上看到友人介紹後，帶同兒子到場，惟發現除介紹的兩個遊樂設施外，場內空空如也，食肆亦寥寥可數，認為「畀人揾笨」。<br />\n<br />\n新田購物城今天起試業，立法會議員黃定光曾稱，216個舖位已租出一半。惟記者今日點算，僅有22間店舖，及吹氣遊樂設施和攤位遊戲有開業。購物城原希望港人及內地顧客各半，但記者在場近兩小時，未見有內地遊客到訪。<br />\n<br />\n有元朗區議員辦本地團，一行約40人到場，惟團友關女士認為，場內店舖與元朗市中心相若，貨品亦沒有比市區便宜，若非朋友邀請及有車接送，她不會到來。惟她指，元朗市中心人流近年每天多到像過年般，希望購物城有助分散人流。<br />\n<br />\n居於九龍區的朱小姐，因看到友人在網上介紹，新田購物城的攤位遊戲及甩尾車遊樂設施，自行開車帶同兒子到場，惟到場後發現除介紹的活動外，沒有其他事情可做，感到「畀人揾笨」。即使有商店已開始營業，她認為店舖類型單調，直言「嚟過一次就夠」。<br />\n<br />\n購物城內今天只有3間食肆開業，其中一店主劉先生指，中午開舖起已有逾50人光顧，有8至9成皆為場內其他店舖的職員，預計今天有100人光顧賺取數千元。他稱對前景感到樂觀，因附近新田車站人流不少，隔鄰停車場亦長期爆滿，認為正式開業後可有更多宣傳，期望半年至一年可以回本。<br />\n<br />\n早前旅遊事務署指，會在新田購物城新增兩個美食車泊位，惟記者未見場內有美食車停泊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8dd6fa41ffd754dcaecf6204ae8f9b06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8dd6fa41ffd754dcaecf6204ae8f9b06.jpg&h=70df948b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8ddc7f35c8ee9b6f9c8b0af30ad9d3c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8ddc7f35c8ee9b6f9c8b0af30ad9d3c6.jpg&h=81d2b268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8ddf3234a5a9184575a6f661faf1450a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8ddf3234a5a9184575a6f661faf1450a.jpg&h=79545044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8de32b0cd8dab0236e9c2308b40780e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8de32b0cd8dab0236e9c2308b40780e3.jpg&h=2686db1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8de77639050213e2228cfcca7917cb5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8de77639050213e2228cfcca7917cb5a.jpg&h=9f89cb1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8df9415fb3a847758da7d80946bfe1b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8df9415fb3a847758da7d80946bfe1b2.jpg&h=fc6234c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180203/s00001/8e01d3fe9ec4e4e1187d326ed65aec2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F8e01d3fe9ec4e4e1187d326ed65aec2f.jpg&h=5fc7fb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180203/s00001/1517650397689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F1517650397689&d=l1IC3F0VMvIjKG%2BDrtaQI9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d2c7b0fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F1517650397689&h=037c41b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180203/s00001/1517650397689</a>"},{"pid":"9464e2b3641ae48eeaaa3b90d3bae47f9908e65c","tid":549380,"uid":20750,"like":783,"dislike":4,"score":